sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User/CI
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.3
    participant Webhook as Validating Webhook<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant Operator as KubeRay Operator<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    participant Registry as Container Registry<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant HeadSvc as Ray Head Service<br/>6379,8265,10001/TCP
    participant HeadPod as Ray Head Pod<br/>GCS + Dashboard
    participant WorkerPods as Ray Worker Pods
    participant Client as Ray Client
    participant ExtClient as External Client
    participant Ingress as Ingress/Route<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant ServeSvc as Ray Serve Service<br/>8000/TCP HTTP
    participant Prom as Prometheus

    %% Flow 1: RayCluster Creation
    rect rgb(230, 240, 255)
        Note over User,WorkerPods: Flow 1: RayCluster Creation
        User->>K8sAPI: POST RayCluster CR<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
        K8sAPI->>Webhook: POST /validate-ray-io-v1-raycluster<br/>Auth: K8s ServiceAccount
        Webhook-->>K8sAPI: Validation Response
        K8sAPI->>Operator: Watch Notification<br/>ServiceAccount Token
        Operator->>K8sAPI: Create Head Pod, Worker Pods, Services<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
        K8sAPI->>Registry: Pull Ray Image<br/>Auth: Pull Secret
        Registry-->>K8sAPI: Ray Container Image
        K8sAPI-->>Operator: Pods Created
        WorkerPods->>HeadPod: Connect to GCS<br/>6379/TCP (unencrypted)
    end

    %% Flow 2: Ray Job Submission
    rect rgb(240, 255, 240)
        Note over Client,WorkerPods: Flow 2: Ray Job Submission
        Client->>HeadSvc: Submit Job<br/>10001/TCP (unencrypted)<br/>Auth: None
        HeadSvc->>HeadPod: Forward Request
        Client->>HeadSvc: Check Status<br/>8265/TCP HTTP<br/>Auth: None
        HeadSvc->>HeadPod: Ray Dashboard Request
        HeadPod->>WorkerPods: Task Distribution<br/>6379/TCP (unencrypted)
        WorkerPods->>HeadPod: Task Results<br/>6379/TCP
        HeadPod-->>Client: Job Status/Results
    end

    %% Flow 3: Ray Serve Inference
    rect rgb(255, 245, 230)
        Note over ExtClient,WorkerPods: Flow 3: Ray Serve Inference
        ExtClient->>Ingress: POST /predict<br/>HTTPS TLS1.2+<br/>Auth: Application-level
        Ingress->>ServeSvc: Forward Request<br/>8000/TCP HTTP (unencrypted)
        ServeSvc->>HeadPod: Route to Serve Deployment<br/>8000/TCP HTTP
        ServeSvc->>WorkerPods: Route to Serve Deployment<br/>8000/TCP HTTP
        WorkerPods-->>ServeSvc: Inference Response
        ServeSvc-->>Ingress: HTTP Response
        Ingress-->>ExtClient: HTTPS Response
    end

    %% Flow 4: Operator Reconciliation
    rect rgb(255, 240, 245)
        Note over Operator,Prom: Flow 4: Operator Reconciliation
        Operator->>K8sAPI: List/Watch Ray CRs<br/>443/TCP HTTPS<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
        Operator->>HeadPod: Health Check Ray Dashboard<br/>8265/TCP HTTP<br/>Auth: None
        HeadPod-->>Operator: Cluster Status
        Prom->>Operator: Scrape Metrics<br/>8080/TCP HTTP<br/>Auth: None
        Operator-->>Prom: Operator Metrics
    end
